[SPEAKER_00]: I don't want to state this is a this is a this is universally, you know, I'm not necessarily speaking on the mayor's behalf when I say this, but my personal opinion and something I think we strive towards as an organization is to hire the best person for the job.

417
00:42:30,470 --> 00:42:40,514
[SPEAKER_00]: And that may mean we're hiring somebody who is going to grow and there may not be room for growth in the organization because of the size of the organization.

418
00:42:40,534 --> 00:42:42,055
[SPEAKER_00]: I do seek

419
00:42:42,442 --> 00:42:44,963
[SPEAKER_00]: Miss Cardello going places with her career.

420
00:42:45,103 --> 00:42:49,165
[SPEAKER_00]: She has she came into this organization as an as an auditor.

421
