[SPEAKER_00]: She left this organization very well rounded as a budget manager and a assistant finance director.

422
00:42:56,568 --> 00:42:58,950
[SPEAKER_00]: I think Miss Cardello could do a lot of things with her career.

423
00:42:59,010 --> 00:43:00,630
[SPEAKER_00]: Obviously, this isn't about 1 person.

424
00:43:01,371 --> 00:43:04,212
[SPEAKER_00]: The prior assistant finance director similar.

425
00:43:04,232 --> 00:43:05,733
[SPEAKER_00]: I have no, no.

426
00:43:09,141 --> 00:43:12,809
[SPEAKER_00]: No questions that he will go places and he's doing a lot of.

427
00:43:14,858 --> 00:43:18,400
[SPEAKER_00]: things on the state level himself, he's already taken different positions on the state level.

428
00:43:19,621 --> 00:43:36,310
[SPEAKER_00]: So just to say that, you know, we have, we also are trying very hard to hire the best and sometimes the best, there's no headroom, there's no growth room for them in terms of like, you know, a position between or, you know, sometimes even a director position.

429
00:43:36,370 --> 00:43:38,892
[SPEAKER_00]: So we also have to recognize that as well as the only context.

430
00:43:39,372 --> 00:43:39,592
[SPEAKER_00]: Thank you.

