443
00:45:05,379 --> 00:45:05,820
[SPEAKER_03]: Sounds great.

444
00:45:06,321 --> 00:45:10,790
[SPEAKER_03]: I think the big thing, you know, budget again level funded as best we can.

445
00:45:10,810 --> 00:45:14,256
[SPEAKER_03]: It does look like there's a couple of increases in so explain those first.

446
