449
00:45:50,241 --> 00:46:00,908
[SPEAKER_03]: So absorbing costs for our support help desk, TOS, for six months, Office 365 licensing for six months, and then our cybersecurity products.

450
00:46:01,508 --> 00:46:02,209
[SPEAKER_03]: for six months.

451
00:46:02,229 --> 00:46:14,739
[SPEAKER_03]: And that's where you see the addition of the 70,000 professional services for TOS and the combined 95,000 increase in computer applications for Office 365 and cybersecurity stuff.

