620
00:59:05,710 --> 00:59:09,471
[SPEAKER_09]: So we're going to see the rest of that in the next fiscal year budget.

621
00:59:10,192 --> 00:59:15,153
[SPEAKER_09]: And is there any expectation of, I guess, are these good deals?

622
00:59:15,173 --> 00:59:16,933
[SPEAKER_09]: Is there any way we could address that cost?

623
00:59:23,095 --> 00:59:30,366
[SPEAKER_03]: If you want to have email, you know, say you want to have office apps, you know, make a lot of people happy for a week.

624
00:59:31,147 --> 00:59:33,490
[SPEAKER_03]: Yeah, make me very happy.

625
00:59:33,530 --> 00:59:34,091
[SPEAKER_03]: I'll tell you that.

626
00:59:36,089 --> 00:59:38,210
[SPEAKER_03]: Someone said to me, well, did you see my email?

627
00:59:38,230 --> 00:59:38,971
[SPEAKER_03]: I'm like, no, I haven't.

628
00:59:39,011 --> 00:59:40,552
[SPEAKER_03]: It's like, well, you got to read my email.

629
00:59:40,572 --> 00:59:44,435
[SPEAKER_03]: I'm like, well, if you needed an immediate answer, why'd you use such a slow mode of communication?

630
00:59:45,876 --> 00:59:48,237
[SPEAKER_03]: But yeah, so there's not much you can do.

631
00:59:48,277 --> 00:59:49,918
[SPEAKER_03]: We're golden Microsoft, right?

632
00:59:49,938 --> 00:59:52,660
[SPEAKER_03]: They're announcing new pricing in July.

633
00:59:52,680 --> 00:59:57,744
[SPEAKER_03]: So we're all kind of sitting and waiting how much they're going to get us for this time.

634
00:59:59,391 --> 01:00:01,393
[SPEAKER_03]: The same thing for our cybersecurity products.

635
01:00:01,694 --> 01:00:04,197
[SPEAKER_03]: They don't go up a lot year-to-year, which is good.

636
01:00:05,318 --> 01:00:10,484
[SPEAKER_03]: Fortunately, we go through a reseller, which buys them in bulk, so they can really press the pricing.

637
01:00:11,726 --> 01:00:14,249
[SPEAKER_03]: They can walk away to a different vendor if they don't like it.

638
01:00:14,749 --> 01:00:15,711
[SPEAKER_03]: It's not much you can do.

639
01:00:15,771 --> 01:00:17,533
[SPEAKER_03]: The only thing you can do is go to Google Suite.

640
01:00:18,427 --> 01:00:19,588
[SPEAKER_03]: or your Microsoft Office.

641
01:00:19,668 --> 01:00:21,169
[SPEAKER_03]: Those are your two choices in the world.

642
01:00:23,090 --> 01:00:29,394
[SPEAKER_03]: Some other things, we did lower costs, like Adobe costs we cut in half last year by changing our licensing structure.

643
01:00:29,434 --> 01:00:30,435
[SPEAKER_03]: What were you using?

644
01:00:31,756 --> 01:00:32,416
[SPEAKER_03]: That type of thing.

645
01:00:33,457 --> 01:00:35,838
[SPEAKER_03]: I'm always reviewing those sort of things every year when it comes up.

646
