01:02:30,695 --> 01:02:33,576
[SPEAKER_03]: as I'm going through, so I generally buy hardware twice a year.

676
01:02:33,596 --> 01:02:37,257
[SPEAKER_03]: So it'll be like, you know, a big purchase maybe about late fall.

