01:03:20,513 --> 01:03:22,374
[SPEAKER_03]: What's the point of asking for that money now?

686
01:03:22,854 --> 01:03:27,316
[SPEAKER_03]: I'll just wait and do it out of my budget later on, on the next fiscal year's budget or what have you.

687
01:03:27,596 --> 01:03:29,977
[SPEAKER_03]: So, but yes, very observant.

688
01:03:29,997 --> 01:03:35,360
[SPEAKER_03]: That is what generally what happens to me between April and June is when I get hit with all my bills, basically.

689
01:03:37,140 --> 01:03:39,081
[SPEAKER_09]: All right, thank you.

690
01:03:39,441 --> 01:03:43,103
[SPEAKER_09]: And my only final question, when are we

