692
01:03:45,897 --> 01:03:46,517
[SPEAKER_09]: What are you thinking?

693
01:03:47,237 --> 01:03:50,799
[SPEAKER_03]: We're actually going to get rid of Wi-Fi because it causes nothing but problems in my life.

694
01:03:55,000 --> 01:03:56,321
[SPEAKER_03]: So City Hall is tough.

695
