[SPEAKER_03]: See, now what he's not telling you, Emily, is that he has a cable he can plug into up there.

712
01:05:18,522 --> 01:05:20,583
[SPEAKER_03]: It's the rest of you on the floor that get nothing.

713
01:05:22,324 --> 01:05:22,645
[SPEAKER_09]: Sad.

714
01:05:23,945 --> 01:05:25,166
[SPEAKER_09]: You've exposed me, Rich.

715
01:05:25,186 --> 01:05:25,927
[SPEAKER_09]: I have.

716
01:05:26,948 --> 01:05:30,290
