01:05:59,350 --> 01:06:01,691
[SPEAKER_03]: Next time you're in the day, come find me.

726
01:06:01,731 --> 01:06:02,111
[SPEAKER_03]: I'll show you.

727
01:06:02,751 --> 01:06:04,412
[SPEAKER_09]: I will not annoy Emily anymore.

728
01:06:04,432 --> 01:06:08,534
[SPEAKER_09]: Okay.

729
01:06:12,936 --> 01:06:16,457
[SPEAKER_09]: Any other questions for Rich Lane about the IT budget?

730
01:06:21,517 --> 01:06:26,943
[SPEAKER_09]: All right, seeing none, Madam Chief of Staff, do you have any general updates?

731
01:06:27,364 --> 01:06:34,532
[SPEAKER_09]: Are we gonna try to schedule a meeting or two next week, or are we looking at two weeks out for our next departmental budget meetings?

732
01:06:36,240 --> 01:06:37,701
[SPEAKER_00]: Thank you president bears.

733
01:06:37,721 --> 01:06:42,565
[SPEAKER_00]: I, yes, I was actually going to communicate with you to see if we could.

734
01:06:43,505 --> 01:06:48,229
[SPEAKER_00]: Basically, have the Wednesday meeting and forego the Tuesday meeting.

735
01:06:48,289 --> 01:06:50,711
[SPEAKER_00]: It would make sense just considering the gap.

736
01:06:50,731 --> 01:06:51,752
[SPEAKER_00]: We're still working through.

737
01:06:53,253 --> 01:06:55,474
[SPEAKER_00]: So that would be the request and.

738
01:06:56,435 --> 01:07:00,976
[SPEAKER_00]: Other than that, we're working with schools to try to understand where their gap remains today.

739
01:07:01,036 --> 01:07:05,577
[SPEAKER_00]: We're working through our budgets to try to fill the gap that we have on our side as well.

740
01:07:06,037 --> 01:07:11,039
[SPEAKER_00]: Try to see if we can find more money for schools, continue to work through to see if we can find money for MFN.

741
01:07:11,159 --> 01:07:13,319
[SPEAKER_00]: I know that's a mayor and council priority.

742
01:07:14,779 --> 01:07:15,080
[SPEAKER_09]: All right.

743
01:07:16,540 --> 01:07:16,960
[SPEAKER_09]: Well, thank you.

744
01:07:17,040 --> 01:07:19,281
[SPEAKER_09]: I think Wednesday next week should work.

745
01:07:19,741 --> 01:07:21,481
[SPEAKER_09]: We'll coordinate exact timing on that meeting.

746
01:07:22,261 --> 01:07:22,481
[SPEAKER_00]: Great.

747
01:07:23,101 --> 01:07:23,362
[SPEAKER_00]: Great.

748
01:07:23,422 --> 01:07:24,022
[SPEAKER_00]: Thank you very much.

749
